":"text","text":"If your offering is a grain offering prepared in a pan, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 7:9","book":"Lev","chapter":7,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" it is to be made of fine flour with oil. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lv 7:9","book":"Lev","chapter":7,"verse":9}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Lev:2:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"When you bring to the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" the grain offering made in any of these ways, it is to be presented to the priest, and he will take it to the altar. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Lev:2:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The priest will remove the memorial portion "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit portion of it"},{"kind":"text","text":" from the grain offering and burn it on the altar, a food offering, a pleasing aroma to the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":". "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit portion of it"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Lev:2:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But the rest of the grain offering will belong to Aaron and his sons; "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 7:9","book":"Lev","chapter":7,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" it is the holiest part of the food offerings to the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lv 7:9","book":"Lev","chapter":7,"verse":9}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Lev:2:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“No grain offering that you present to the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" is to be made with yeast, for you are not to burn "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Some Hb mss, Sam, LXX, Tg read present"},{"kind":"text","text":" any yeast "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 12:14","book":"Exo","chapter":12,"verse":14,"letter":"a"},{"ki